{"tid":828014,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"窮到要食二手飯..","createTime":"2018-09-19T11:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T14:33:11.000Z","uid":22589,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"503e063fc7af07040ce91e24752c8b7a4b9798e4","tid":828014,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會忘記昨晚.. <br />\n<br />\n我已經四日沒有東西落肚，昨晚終於忍不住，真的很肚餓，餓到連尊嚴也不顧... <br />\n沒有辦法，身上已無分文，屋企人又唔理，又找不到工作，連八達通的五十蚊按金也拿走了.. <br />\n<br />\n吃二手飯的感覺真的很難堪，昨晚在某屋村的大家樂，吃了別人剩下的飯餸，理不了別人的目光，一邊食眼淚俏俏的在眼角滴下......我是一個窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6931682bcf425cbe5f7740bda7cdfd40ce7621eb","tid":828014,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:08:52.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的"},{"pid":"095ce62a013df553522bb9d51764ff7608961fc6","tid":828014,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"瑞和街街市?"},{"pid":"7bdac55a2f3453849ccf28b8455a227d6a4f2523","tid":828014,"uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"095ce62a013df553522bb9d51764ff7608961fc6","tid":828014,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"瑞和街街市?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"裕_坊"},{"pid":"deed2598b72c66a35757183530cb34a65b69c2bc","tid":828014,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6931682bcf425cbe5f7740bda7cdfd40ce7621eb","tid":828014,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:08:52.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b5fb8dc8e5492add63487ec43afd3c43764a33","tid":828014,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"平時去開中環果間食OL d二手飯"},{"pid":"9673d7490a6c79b4718c3bf6f67dcd87fae10a4f","tid":828014,"uid":22589,"like":0,"d